Rig Locator System




The Rig Locator is intended as a service to our customers. Patterson-UTI does not warrant the accuracy or completeness of the content, which may not reflect real-time data. The Rig Locator information is not intended to be, and should not be used as, a basis for making an investment decision regarding Patterson-UTI securities.
Welcome to the Patterson-UTI Rig Locator, your source of inventory and location information about Patterson-UTI drilling rigs. 
This system is designed to assist you in quickly finding a rig to meet your drilling needs. Once you make a selection contact the regional office to schedule delivery.
A breakdown of our operating rigs can be viewed on our Rig Summary page.


