  Home  Stocks  dividend announcements  Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTEN) announces a quarterly dividend of $0.02     Stocksdividend announcements  Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTEN) announces a quarterly dividend of $0.02  ByME Staff -July 27, 2017 0  Share on Facebook
Tweet on Twitter


 Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTEN) to go ex-dividend.On 7/27/2017 Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc. ( NASDAQ:PTEN ) announced that it will be issuing a quarterly dividend in the amount of $0.02 up from $0.02 making the yield .Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTEN) Ex- dividend datePatterson-UTI Energy, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTEN) is set to go ex-dividend on and will be payable on 9/21/2017 Dividend History for Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTEN) The next payable dividend for Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc. is scheduled for 9/21/2017. There is an annual dividend of $$0.08 with a yield of 0.41% The payout ration for the trailing 12 months of earnings is -3.83% , -8.00% based on this years estimates and -133.33% based on next years projected estimates.Recent Dividend History for Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTEN) 

